p: \b\pn, get back over here! We need to talk!
\b\pn, it's great to see you again!
\bI'm sure the boss filled you in, but we've found some ancient grove of Pokemon.
\bIf we're lucky, we might find a really rare Pokemon here.
\bSee if you can find it, and maybe challenge it to a battle!
\bBe warned though- you might not be able to catch it, or even find it.
\bWe've got the choppers, all that's left is you!
\bWe need footage of you battling, so get going!
\bI can't believe I got to see a legendary Pokemon!
\bWe're going to see if we can track where that Latios went... and if we do, we'll be sure to call you again!
\rIt's all right, \pn. We'll find a way to find that Latios again!
